fundProfile.description: Tesla, Inc. designs, develops, manufactures, leases, and sells electric vehicles, and energy generation and storage systems in the United States, China, and internationally. The company's Automotive segment offers electric vehicles, as well as sells automotive regulatory credits. It services its vehicles and sells used vehicles. The Energy Generation and Storage segment offers solar energy generation and storage products, leases solar energy systems, and sells solar electricity. Tesla also provides vehicle insurance and maintenance services, as well as owns its sales and service network.
